OL,3,CGirl's sudden death prompts family's
OL,4,Cfight for nationwide heart screenings
OL,6,FParents who have lost their children
OL,7,Fto undiagnosed heart conditions are
OL,8,Fcalling on the government to introduce
OL,9,Froutine heart screenings for younger
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FStudent Anja Wilson, from Bradford,
OL,13,Fhad just finished her A-levels and was
OL,14,Fexcited to study biology at university
OL,15,Fwhen she died due to a hereditary
OL,16,Felectrical issue with her heart which
OL,17,Fshe did not know she had.
