OL,3,CGirl's sudden death prompts family's
OL,4,Cfight for nationwide heart screenings
OL,6,FThe 19-year-old was found in her bed
OL,7,Flast year by her mother Carly, shortly
OL,8,Fafter she had been to doctors
OL,9,Fcomplaining of her heart racing.
OL,11,FAnja was sent home with a monitor -
OL,12,Fbut did not live to see the results.
OL,14,FCarly and father Kev have since raised
OL,15,Fthousands to provide heart screenings
OL,16,Fto young people in their area, but are
OL,17,Fcalling on the government to do the
OL,18,Fsame nationwide to prevent future
OL,19,Fdeaths.
