OL,3,CGirl's sudden death prompts family's
OL,4,Cfight for nationwide heart screenings
OL,6,F"The more people we can screen, the
OL,7,Fmore impact we can have," said Kev.
OL,9,F"Every life is precious but even more
OL,10,Fso the young and the future of the
OL,11,Fcountry."
OL,13,FRecounting the morning in question,
OL,14,Fdad Kev said he remembers Carly's
OL,15,F"guttural" scream as she realised what
OL,16,Fhad happened.
