OL,3,CGirl's sudden death prompts family's
OL,4,Cfight for nationwide heart screenings
OL,6,FOut of their grief they have gone on
OL,7,Fto set up The Beat Goes On 31, funding
OL,8,Fcardiac screening for young people
OL,9,Faged 14 to 35.
OL,11,FSteve said: "Our campaign started when
OL,12,Fwe realised this was a national
OL,13,Fproblem, it's not just in Scunthorpe."
OL,15,FFour in five young people who die from
OL,16,Fheart conditions like Nathan's do not
OL,17,Fhave any apparent symptoms.
OL,19,F"The government don't seem to be
OL,20,Ftaking any action," he added. "They've
OL,21,Fbeen debating this for 20 years."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
