OL,3,CGirl's sudden death prompts family's
OL,4,Cfight for nationwide heart screenings
OL,6,FAnja's family meanwhile have now all
OL,7,Fundergone screenings at Leeds General
OL,8,FInfirmary, including 17-year-old
OL,9,Fsister Isabelle, with both Carly and
OL,10,FKev learning they too have the
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FDr Steven Cox, the CEO for the charity
OL,14,FCardiac Risk in the Young, said the
OL,15,Fdemand for screening was
OL,16,F"unbelievable".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
