OL,3,CGirl's sudden death prompts family's
OL,4,Cfight for nationwide heart screenings
OL,6,F"We have over 130,000 people who have
OL,7,Fregistered an interest to be screened
OL,8,Fso we're really struggling to respond
OL,9,Fto the demand for people to be
OL,10,Ftested," he said.
OL,12,F"We have to do something proactive
OL,13,Fidentify these young people at risk."
OL,15,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "We would like to
OL,17,Fexpress our heartfelt sympathy to
OL,18,FSteve and Gill following the loss of
OL,19,Ftheir son Nathan.
